OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780916574
OL,3,CTech companies face new laws if they
OL,4,Cdo not act on stop child explicit
OL,5,Cimages
OL,7,FHe went on to praise the companies,
OL,8,Fsaying they "are some of the most
OL,9,Finnovative companies in the world" and
OL,10,Fshared his belief that they can help
OL,11,Fsolve the issues facing young people
OL,12,Fonline.
OL,14,FThe prime minister said that the speed
OL,15,Fof technological change cannot be an
OL,16,Fexcuse for harm and said the
OL,17,Fgovernment would act "quickly" and
OL,18,F"firmly".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/3
